    </ul>


            <ol class="list-numbers recipe-directions__list" itemprop="recipeInstructions">
                        <li class="step" ng-class="{'finished': stepIsActive0}" ng-click="stepIsActive0 = !stepIsActive0"><span class="recipe-directions__list--item">Place bacon into a skillet over medium heat, and cook until crisp. Remove, and drain on paper towels.</span></li>
                        <li class="step" ng-class="{'finished': stepIsActive1}" ng-click="stepIsActive1 = !stepIsActive1"><span class="recipe-directions__list--item">Place the cream cheese in a bowl, and beat until light and fluffy. Stir in the Cheddar cheese, Monterey Jack cheese, mayonnaise, salt, pepper, garlic powder, pimentos, onion, jalapeno, and cayenne pepper until well blended.</span></li>
                        <li class="step" ng-class="{'finished': stepIsActive2}" ng-click="stepIsActive2 = !stepIsActive2"><span class="recipe-directions__list--item">Spread two bread slices with the cream cheese mixture. Top each slice with avocado and bacon, divided evenly. Top with two remaining bread slices to make a sandwich. Cut each sandwich in half to serve.</span></li>
            </ol>
